creator: Vibo
descriptionHtml:
Vibo is the place where all event participants can collaborate in order to plan the music and timeline for their special event, whether it’s a big wedding or small party. Join an event created by your DJ using a link, add songs you love to different sections of your event, and invite your guests to add their musical touch to the sections that are public, so that your DJ can feel the vibe of your party ahead of time.

Use Vibo to:

Build a timeline for your event and add the songs you love with or without your guests

Add Likes, Must Play, Don’t Play and Comments to songs so your DJ knows what songs are important to you

Personalize your event with a cover photo and share it with your guests so they can collaborate with you on specific sections of your event

Add song by searching, importing from Spotify, pasting links, or find new ideas in the curated lists
Easily listen to songs on music services you already use including YouTube, Spotify, Apple Music, Deezer, Tidal, iTunes and more

We hope you enjoy using Vibo and that you find the planning process just as much fun as the event itself!
Stop by and learn more at https://vibodj.com Having trouble?
Please reach out to support@vibodj.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We added some UI improvements and fixes.

Any feedback is always welcome at support@vibodj.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Timeline screen redesign
- Added headlines with custom colors
- Divided all section settings into separate groups
- Added “Make this section a headline” switch to support headlines
- Inactive settings are now visually disabled to avoid confusion
Assigning more than one DJ to an event is now supported
- Event name, DJ notes, date and location can be added to Google calendar
